\subsection{[[setwide()]] and [[squeeze()]]}

%claude:
[<setwide()>] sets [[addr1,addr2]] to span the whole buffer
(line~1 to [<dol>]) when the user did not supply explicit addresses
(which can be checked by inspecting the global [<given>]).
% will see explicit address in Section~X

<<function [[setwide]](ed.c)>>=
/// main -> commands('r') -> <>
