%claude:
Writing (as in [[w foo.txt]]) is the dual of reading. [<putfile()>] 
called below iterates over the
address range, fetches each line from [[tfile]] via [<getline()>],
and writes it to the output file via [[Bputrune()]] (from [[libbio]]).
The [[W]] (uppercase) variant opens the file in append mode.

