% when writing in tfile so probably fine when get it back.

% this is slower than putline which with one write could write many runes;
% here we read one rune at a time, with many read() syscalls, one per rune,
% but fine with kernel buffer cache. Maybe point to block cache opti
% in section X when kernel didn't have such cache in 70's.


